      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "上川郁実",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ikumi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ですが、今のみなさんはまるで別のグループに見えます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ you all look like a completely different group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5414197125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "上川郁実",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ikumi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一体どんな時間を過ごしたのかと不思議に思うくらいに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me wonder what kind of time you all have spent together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
