      "startTime": 136.708089431
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 136.9409293968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに言われてみると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.8414105572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "五人の時は、なんだかんだで琴乃ちゃんが\nなんとかしてくれる……と思っていたかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we had five members‚ one way or another‚ we thought\nthat Kotono-chan would pull through for us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0860467824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "私達四人だって全力で頑張ってきましたわ\nまぁ、それでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We four have been doing our best!\nBut even so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.7563821813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん。心の中で、琴乃ちゃんに甘えちゃってたのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Maybe we were relying on Kotono-chan in our hearts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5480260052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。でも、私達は変われた……\n変わってきたんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But we’ve changed…\nI think we’ve been changing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7480427264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんがいなくなった時点で\n五人の時と同じ意識ではいられませんでしたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once Kotono-chan was gone‚\nwe couldn’t keep the same mindset as when we had five.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "五人の時と比べて、圧倒的に\n危機感が大きくなりましたものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We definitely had a much stronger\nsense of crisis compared to when we had five.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "私も、沙季ちゃんも、芽衣ちゃんも、すずちゃんも……\n自分が月ストを支えるんだって強く意識してたと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we all—me‚ Saki-chan‚ Mei-chan‚ and Suzu-chan—\nwere strongly aware that we had to support Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.5892075423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、だからSNSを見た時に\nそれぞれの感想が増えてたんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ maybe that’s why when we looked at social media‚\nthere were more comments about each of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.7821463743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 195.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "それですわ！　きっと私達のパフォーマンスに滲み出た\n覚悟が伝わったのですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it! Our resolve must have\nshown through in our performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.2475284055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "五人の時は、琴乃ちゃんを中心とした一糸乱れぬ\nパフォーマンスを持ち味にしていたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we had five‚ our strength was our perfectly synchronized\nperformance centered around Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "でも今は、五人の時とだいぶ違うよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ it’s quite different from when we had five.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.9270048298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく手応えがあったんですから\nきちんと言語化して次に繋げたいですね。うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we’ve gotten such a good response‚\nI want to put it into words properly and connect it to our next step. Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ。私が以前千紗とユニットを組んだ時は\n最終的にお互いに目立とうとしたのが功を奏したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s right. When I formed a unit with Chisa before‚\nwhat ultimately worked in our favor was trying to stand out from each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "今の月ストは沙季ちゃんと千紗ちゃんのユニットと\n通じるものがあるってことかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re saying that the current Moon Tempest\nis similar to your and Chisa-chan’s unit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_05-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……なんというか、四人それぞれが\n殻を破ったような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right… It’s like the four of us\nhave broken out of our shells…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
