      "text": "内なる野生を解き放つことで、パフォーマンスが\n向上した、といったところでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our performance has improved\nby unleashing our inner wildness‚ I guess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
